 LANDED cluster refactor LOCK V1 GATE FINAL). LOCK 1 Pre-Beta FULL strict cumulative cross-chat preserved invariant cumulative + LOCK 2 Daniel Gates 100% strict library 657/657 100% gate ACHIEVED preserved invariant + **Big 11 engine layer 8/8 phases LANDED COMPLETE FINAL gate închis NEW**.\n\n**Safety conditions cluster cross-chat 14 birou implementation progress: LOCK 4 Medical Disclaimer LANDED `ecd71a7` + LOCK 8 Kcal Floor 1200 BN filter LANDED `51728bc` chat-current ACASĂ post-evening cumulative**.\n\n**LOCK 4 Medical Safety Disclaimer + T&C Mandatory Accept Onboarding Gate LANDED `ecd71a7` pre-onboarding gate first-launch implementation Co-CTO autonomous PROMPT_CC** chat-current ACASĂ post-evening. 6 files (4 NEW `src/pages/disclaimer/` module + 2 MODIFY `src/main.js` + `src/state.js:29` enum extend). Anti-paternalism preserved invariant ABSOLUTE (NU blocăm log user; engine intelligence conservative defaults preserved via existing Periodization + Calibration Tiers + RIR Matrix + Demographic Prior cold-start NU medical knowledge layer NEW). Tests +24 NEW: 3480 → 3504 PASS. **§6 flag legitim:** T&C wording legal review avocat specialist drept consumator + drept medical + GDPR pre-Beta launch finalize RECOMMENDED (extern risk shift NU CEO decision tactical, owner Andura placeholder pending SRL/PFA legal entity formalization Daniel decision deferred per chat strategic).\n\n**LOCK 8 Kcal Floor 1200 Engine #3 Bayesian Nutrition filter LANDED `51728bc` engine-side forward-going infrastructure pre-emptive Co-CTO autonomous PROMPT_CC** chat-current ACASĂ post-evening. **Branch B decided** (V1 vanilla port `src/pages/nutrition.js` NU exista yet — mockup design SoT linii 1801-1832 Edit ✎ pencil pattern existing but NU yet ported v2). 4 files single module `src/engine/bayesianNutrition/` (2 NEW: `observationFilter.js` ~100 LOC pure-function + `tests/observationFilter.test.js` ~200 LOC 21 tests; 2 MODIFY: `constants.js` +37 LOC `KCAL_FLOOR_DAILY_MIN=1200` + `KCAL_FLOOR_CITATION_SOURCE='WHO (Organizatia Mondiala a Sanatatii)'` + `index.js` +13 LOC filter integration pre sample mean/variance computation). ZERO mutation Gaussian Conjugate Prior Normal-Normal closed-form algorithm semantics ADR 026 §9.4.1 A1 LOCKED V1 preserved invariant. Tests +21 NEW: 3504 → 3525 PASS. **§6 flag legitim:** UI nutrition logging port v2 vanilla consumer pending Daniel review explicit chat NEW pre-Beta finalize (forward-going engine filter ready; mockup design SoT existing dar NU yet ported v2; Daniel decision pre-Beta vs defer post-Beta — engine filter already protect calcul obiective + preconizari viitoare).\n\nPending LOCK 9 + LOCK 10 + LOCK 11 sequential implementation post handover chat NEW → Pre-Beta scope LOCK V2 cap-coadă completion gate FINAL post LOCK 11 LANDED → Daniel Gates 100% strict smoke production manual → Bugatti Full Audit pre-Launch GATE FINAL sequencing P5 final.\n\nCross-link [[medical-safety-disclaimer-t-c-mandatory]] amendments 2026-05-15-chat-current-post-evening + [[kcal-floor-1200-engine-filter]] amendments 2026-05-15-chat-current-post-evening + [[../summaries/handover-2026-05-15-chat-acasa-post-evening-triple-landed-c4-8-bayesian-nutrition-plus-lock-4-medical-disclaimer-plus-lock-8-kcal-floor-1200]] §1 NEW summary codify chat-current ACASĂ post-evening cumulative.\n"},{"date":"2026-05-15","note":"APPEND chat ACASĂ 2026-05-15 chat-current post-midnight — **Library 657/657 = 100% gate LOCK V1 ACHIEVED per LOCK 2 Daniel Gates strict cross-chat 14 birou directive verbatim \"100%\"** post Bundle 6.0.7 Core +57 NEW LANDED commit `739a753` Co-CTO autonomous Phase A audit (28 base themes × ~2 avg variants + 1 Option C marginal Dragon Flag/Windshield Wiper/Body Saw Plank scope expand = 57 NEW exact target hit). Schema 600 → **657/657 = 100% gate ACHIEVED** cumulative cross-chat 14 birou cumulative directive LOCK 2. Core canonical V1 entries 0 → 57 (reserved invariant Bundle 6.0.1-6.0.6 → unlocked Bundle 6.0.7). Cascade 100% resolved (342/342 refs) + tier distribution mixed + equipment canonical 6 valid + ZERO mutation existing 600 entries (HARD CONSTRAINT §F3.12 strict).\n\n**Big 11 engine layer progression cap-coadă ADR_ENGINE_REFACTOR §4: 3/8 phases LANDED cumulative cross-chat post-evening + post-midnight** (C4.1 Muscle Recovery `35a7a8d` post-evening + C4.2 Weakness Detector `a35d362` post-midnight + C4.3 Periodization `4ed3c2f` post-midnight). C4.4 Specialization + C4.5 Coach Director + C4.6 Cascade Defense + C4.7 Vitality Layer + C4.8 Bayesian Nutrition cap-coadă pending downstream.\n\nLOCK 1 Pre-Beta FULL strict cumulative cross-chat preserved invariant cumulative + LOCK 2 Daniel Gates 100% strict library gate ACHIEVED ✓ (first cumulative LOCK 2 milestone within Pre-Beta scope). Path Forward Post-Big-11-LANDED cumulative: implementation safety conditions cluster cross-chat 14 birou LOCKED V1 (Medical Disclaimer + T&C Mandatory + Kcal Floor 1200 + Aggressive Loading Warning + ADR 033 MMI promote SPEC READY V1 + F5 AA-Friction Modal UX iteration) + C5 session sequence ordering implementation engine-side + Calendar engine-side + smoke production manual Daniel test cu Firebase + PWA + telefon + Bugatti Full Audit pre-Launch GATE FINAL.\n\nCross-link [[../summaries/handover-2026-05-15-chat-acasa-post-midnight-triple-landed-bundle-6-0-7-plus-c4-2-plus-c4-3]] codify chat-current ACASĂ post-midnight cumulative + [[bugatti-audit-nuclear-pre-launch]] §1 LOCK V1 reaffirm + [[autonomy-paradigm-v1]] amendments 2026-05-15 10th consecutive cross-chat directive verbatim. Vault meta-tooling acest /wiki-ingest doc-only ZERO src/ touched per HARD CONSTRAINTS §F3.12 strict — Bundle 6.0.7 + C4.2 + C4.3 src/ touched separate atomic commits Bugatti single-concern. Co-CTO autonomy MAXIMUM 10th consecutive cross-chat directive verbatim trust delegation MAXIMUM preserved invariant.\n"},{"date":"2026-05-14-evening","note":"APPEND chat ACASĂ 2026-05-14 evening end-of-chat scribe-mode — **Bugatti Full Audit pre-Launch LOCK V1 NEW** cumulative integration sequencing P5 final pre-Launch GATE FINAL. Daniel CEO directive verbatim chat-current evening *\"dupa smoke test la launch o sa facem un audit nuclear ca cel din trecut, chiar mai extended... va fi bugatti audit. Poate sa dureze 20000 ore, I don't care... no dead code, all good, all runing etc\"* + clarify scope re-LOCK *\"nu. FULL AUDIT. Fiecare linie de cod citita, fiecare virgula, TOT. Si dupa smoke test fix inainte de beta. App latest landed\"* = sequencing post-update final pre-Launch (1 Tot tracks 100% LANDED LOCK 1 cascade → 2 Daniel Gates smoke production manual LOCK 2 cascade → 3 Bugatti Full Audit Co-CTO every line cod + every virgulă + TOT pe latest commit LANDED LOCK V1 NEW evening → 4 Fix ALL issues surfaced → 5 Beta launch). Acceptance criteria peak craft Bugatti pur cumulative cu LOCK 1 Pre-Beta FULL strict + LOCK 2 Daniel Gates 100% strict + Bugatti FULL QUALITY no EXCUSES 13j preserved invariant cross-chat 2026-05-13j → 14 birou → 14 evening crescente. NEW concept page [[bugatti-audit-nuclear-pre-launch]] codify chat-current evening + NEW summary [[../summaries/handover-2026-05-14-evening-bugatti-full-audit-lock-plus-2-co-cto-halucinatii-recovery]] cross-link bidirectional. Audit GATE FINAL pre-Beta NU intermediar NU optional. Cumulative wiki count 137 → 139 chat-current evening (+1 NEW concept + 1 NEW summary). Tests 3318 PASS preserved EXACT (Bundle 6.0.5 Arms +38 NEW tests LANDED commit chain `281bfe2` → `ef678c2` 8 atomic single-concern Bugatti pushed origin). Co-CTO autonomy MAXIMUM 8th consecutive cross-chat directive verbatim trust delegation MAXIMUM preserved invariant."}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/concepts/pre-beta-full-scope-lock-v2.md"},
